dict.string: I also enjoy teaching people about programming...
I am programming mentor in FRC: First Robotics Competition, where I teached highschool students how to use LabView and how to program in Java.
I love those kids. I even design them their logos.
I've also been asked by some teachers to give special workshops for middle school students about iOS programming in Objective-C.
I'm trying to master Swift 100% so I can start teaching them.
